values: My journal has been inactive for some time now, but I have chosen not to take it down for several reasons. I have friends journals who I like to read, I like to participate in the live journal communities sometimes, and finally I think I may want to come back to my journal at some point in time...
For various reasons my journal is now "friends only." This means you will not be able to read my journal unless I add you to my "friends" list.
